<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Manic Madhouse DTF Designs</title>

<style>

body{
font-family:Arial;
margin:0;
background:#0f0f0f;
color:white;
}

header{
background:#ff007a;
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
}

.logo{
height:80px;
display:block;
margin:0 auto 10px;
}

nav a{
color:white;
margin:0 15px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
background:#111;
padding:60px;
text-align:center;
}

.section{
padding:40px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
gap:15px;
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
}

.card{
background:#1b1b1b;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
}

form{
max-width:500px;
margin:auto;
}

input,select,textarea{
width:100%;
padding:10px;
margin:8px 0;
border-radius:6px;
border:none;
}

button{
background:#7b2cff;
color:white;
padding:12px;
border:none;
border-radius:6px;
width:100%;
}

footer{
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
background:#111;
margin-top:40px;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>

<img src="logo.png" class="logo">

<h1>Manic Madhouse DTF Designs</h1>

<nav>
<a href="#designs">Designs</a>
<a href="#order">Custom Order</a>
<a href="#press">Instructions</a>
</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<h2>Custom DTF Transfers Made To Order</h2>

<p>Upload your design or request one of our premade transfers.</p>

</section>

<section class="section" id="designs">

<h2>Popular Designs</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">Chaos But Make It Cute</div>
<div class="card">Hot Mess Express</div>
<div class="card">Overstimulated Moms Club</div>
<div class="card">Emotionally Support Cowgirl</div>
<div class="card">Running On Coffee</div>
<div class="card">Welcome To The Madhouse</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section" id="order">

<h2>Request Custom Order</h2>

<form action="https://formspree.io/f/yourformid" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">

<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name" required>
<input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required>

<input type="file" name="design">

<select name="size">
<option>Pocket</option>
<option>8 inch</option>
<option>10 inch</option>
<option>12 inch</option>
<option>Oversized</option>
</select>

<input type="number" name="quantity" placeholder="Quantity">

<textarea name="notes" placeholder="Details"></textarea>

<button type="submit">Request Quote</button>

</form>

</section>

<section class="section" id="press">

<h2>DTF Press Instructions</h2>

<p>Temperature: 305°F – 320°F</p>
<p>Press Time: 10–15 seconds</p>
<p>Pressure: Medium / Firm</p>

<p>1. Pre-press garment 5 seconds</p>
<p>2. Place transfer</p>
<p>3. Press 10-15 seconds</p>
<p>4. Let cool completely</p>
<p>5. Peel film</p>
<p>6. Re-press 5 seconds</p>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© Manic Madhouse DTF Designs</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
